ISLAMABAD, Feb 8 (APP): President Dr. Arif Alvi along with his wife Samina Alvi extended condolences to Prime Minister’s Special Assistant Dr. Sania Nishtar on the death of her mother.
They expressed deep sorrow over the passing away of Dr Nishtar’s mother and prayed for the departed soul to rest in peace.
